-- Sarkozy expects Eurogroup to have ambitious plan
-- 
-- Sun Oct 12, 2008 9:40am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/12/us-financial-sarkozy-idUSTRE49B20420081012

 

 PARIS  (Reuters) - French President Nicolas Sarkozy said on Sunday he expected the leaders of euro zone countries would come up with an "ambitious and coordinated plan" to tackle the financial crisis. 

 Speaking to reporters ahead of a meeting of the 15 euro zone leaders, Sarkozy said he would announce some specific French measures for the domestic banking sector on Monday. (Reporting by Emmanuel Jarry; Editing by  Crispian Balmer )